[SDG-TERM]: sdgfetch and sdgtip run automatically on every new terminal window
[SDG-TERM]: Use tipme to get a random SDG-OS tip from any terminal
[SDG-TERM]: eza aliases ls, la, ll, lt give colourful directory listings with icons
[SDG-TERM]: zoxide lets you cd <partial> to jump to any directory — even partial matches work
[SDG-TERM]: Use plz to re-run the last command with sudo
[SDG-TERM]: Split panes in Ghostty with Alt+Arrow keys
[SDG-TERM]: Search your command history with cmdhist (uses fzf)
[SDG-TERM]: Reload Ghostty config with Ctrl+R — no restart needed
[SDG-TERM]: Use microfind for fuzzy file search that opens the selection in micro
